metadata.name: "CHOOSE YOURSELF…"
metadata.description:
In this strange world...we put on masks...create avatars...invent unusual creatures that could reflect our essence…

But suddenly the best character...the best picture of your profile is you...you just need to choose what you will be today, tomorrow or in the future…

Try to choose yourself…create your own story…

(30 unique images joined together on one canvas...different materials were used...canvas, paints, glue, fire, plastic, water, sun rays...and time...exactly 100 days have passed since the start of the work...and now it is completed…)
